---
title: Caribbean Chicken & Roasted Veggies with Cucumber Salad & Mayonnaise
description: We're using our mild Caribbean jerk seasoning to give the classic combo of chicken and veggies some Jamaican mojo.
Colourful veggies with salad and creamy mayo bring added excitement to this devilishly delicious dish.

